â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€• yeahyank - View the Yank information page. yeahyenominations - View all the possible yenominations; this includes limiteds. yeahbalance <userid> - View a given user's Yank account. yeahbalance yank - View the yank and yEAh Games' financing and budget details. yeahdeposit - Request money be deposited into your account. yeahwithdraw - Request money be withdrawn from your account. yeahrates - View all the current rates; exchange rates, yax rates, yoan rates, conversion rates, yinterest rates. yeahstockmarket - View all information relating to the stock market: how it works, FAQs, and a short description. yeahstocks [company name] - View the current, up-to-date information on that company's stocks: its share price, number of shares, shares for sale, holders, etc. yeahinvest - Invest in a company's shares! yeahsell - Sell your holdings back to the yank. yeahsell private - Sell your holdings privately, with a custom price.
Music
â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€•â€• Note: These requests will be answered by @yEAh 2.0. music.play [link or search/title] - The bot will automatically join a voice channel that you are in and play the audio requested; if there is already an audio playing, yours will be put into a queue. The bot will either play a link from the web or, if you use a title, it will search the web and play the closest result (see the list here for both options). music.join - The bot will join your voice channel; it will not play any audio until it is requested. music.loop - The bot will loop the currently-playing audio. music.skip - Skips the current audio and moves to the next in the queue. music.leave - Kicks the bot from the voice channel and stops the audio. PLEASE USE yeah2help TO CONTINUE TO THE NEXT PAGE!

yEAh 2.0 BOT 08-Apr-22 07:22 PM
Yet another music bot. Music: join Joins a voice channel. leave Clears the queue and leaves the voice channel. loop Loops the currently playing song. now Displays the currently playing song. pause Pauses the currently playing song. play Plays a song. queue Shows the player's queue. remove Removes a song from the queue at a given index. resume Resumes a currently paused song. shuffle Shuffles the queue. skip Vote to skip a song. The requester can automatically skip. stop Stops playing song and clears the queue. summon Summons the bot to a voice channel. volume Sets the volume of the player. â€‹No Category: help Shows this message Type music.help command for more info on a command. You can also type music.help category for more info on a category.
